<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM8.6">
<l>cuṟṟamellām piṉṟoṭarat tolkāṉa maṭaintavaṉē</l>
<l>yaṟṟavarkaṭ karumaruntē yayōttinakark katipatiyē</l>
<l>kaṟṟavarkaḷ tāmvāḻuṅ kaṇapuratteṉ karumaṇiyē</l>
<l>ciṟṟavaitaṉ coṟkoṇṭa cīrāmā tālēlō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You who reached the ancient forest as all the kinsmen followed behind!</l>
<l>O rare Remedy to the renouncers! O King of the city of Ayodhyā!</l>
<l>O Apple of my eye from Kaṇapuram, where the learned people live!</l>
<l>O Śrīrāma, who accepted the younger stepmother’s word! Tālēlō!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
